        dc:description           "Figure 11. Dicerapanorpa diceras, from Kangding, Sichuan. (A) Male, dorsal view; (B) female, dorsal view (C, D) genital bulb of male, ventral and dorsal views; (E) aedeagus complex, ventral view; (F) abdominal segments IX–XI of female, lateral view; (G) same, ventral view. Scale bars: A and B = 3.0 mm; C and D = 0.5 mm; E = 0.2 mm; F and G = 0.3 mm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4608139/files/figure.png" .

